svg.text: The core of all the problems of the world is People;
A magazine and the live it advocates.
The core of all the problems of people is Live.
The first paragraph of Inaugural Editorial in the First issue in 1925:

The attitude of this magazine is like, in the leisure Sunday morning every week, invite a few good friends to gather together to talk about something without constraint, that is flexible, relaxing, lively, elegant and interesting.
